  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1403832">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1403832/" class="title-link">更真实的“官场现形记”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1403832"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/QingRen/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1109291-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/QingRen/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">QingRen</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-06-09"
      class="main-meta">2008-06-09 21:12:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1403832_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      这本个人年谱记录的作者参与、听闻的逸闻轶事把道咸年间吏治腐败的丑态描绘得入木三分，当之无愧的“官场现形记”。     从道咸年间的情况可以想象清末将如何糜烂。      另，张对曾国藩颇有微词，从另一个方面看看曾国藩和太平天国，很有意思。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1403832_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1403832_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
