  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1075526">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1075526/" class="title-link">个人见证的历史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1075526"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1256216/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1256216-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1256216/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">alaska</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-09-21"
      class="main-meta">2006-09-21 13:59:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1075526_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  第二任教父麦克说，“所有的事情都是私事。”这本书，记录的正是个人见证的历史。常常，被习惯的公共思维定势左右我们的头脑，实际上，对历史这座矿藏来说，自己发掘的乐趣，远远大过于 参考别人的发现。道咸宦海见闻录，只记载事实，不强加个人的观点，是本好书。史料为王。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1075526_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1075526_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2507921">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2507921/" class="title-link">我读的第一本非白话文书籍</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2507921"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1084678/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1084678/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">愤然子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-12"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-12 13:06:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2507921_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读这本书的源起，是几位清史名家在写道咸朝的历史时都多次引用本书。 书中最有意思的是作者几次外放前召对时和皇帝的对话，非常详尽、完整。虽然明知会有作者的粉饰，但至少能清晰地看到几位皇帝对某些问题的关注点。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中华书局1981版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
